name: Joe and the woodpecker solution
description:
Have a problem with a woodpecker in your trees, Joe's got you covered.

based off of an overheard comment about a neighbor named joe that 'took care' of those pesky woodpeckers.  

three second animated loop
2000 x 2000 | 23.976 fps
